29865.html"><ins>改变了做法</ins></a>。 <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/DimaZeniuk/status/1722799384193032583"><ins>还有这个令人厌恶的视频。</ins></a>自从 2019 年推出这款类似卡车的车辆以来，这无疑是一次漫长而奇怪的旅程。</p><p>当然，Rivian 最近也遇到了自己的问题。该公司在不到一个月的时间里召回了两次，是的两次<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-issues-its-second-airbag-recall-in-less-than-a-month-163154213.html"><ins>安全气囊</ins></a>。它还经历了<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-layoffs-184047174.html"><ins>几轮裁员，</ins></a>这通常不是一个好兆头。然而，这也不全是坏消息，Rivian 正在佐治亚州<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-georgia-incentives-221339799.html"><ins>建造一座耗资 50 亿美元的制造工厂</ins></a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/rivian-now-offers-a-wall-charger-and-2000-install-credit-with-ev-truck-purchases-162252249.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/rivian-now-offers-a-wall-charger-and-2000-install-credit-with-ev-truck-purchases-162252249.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9f87d50d-462f-4019-95d5-6abdc78f3d51</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 16:22:52 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1700238174</ingested><modified> 2023-11-17T16:22:58+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="754" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/cb2864f0-8564-11ee-bc3d-a63e2cd28ced" width="1260"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description